  <brief_title>Clinical Evaluation of the Zynex Blood Volume Monitor (CM-1500) in Healthy Male Adult Subjects During a Blood Draw</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Evaluation of the Zynex Blood Volume Monitor (CM-1500) in Healthy Male Adult Subjects During a Blood Draw</official_title>
